#

Classic Beef Borshch

110 min
$15
300 kcal
Difficulty: 30%
Servings: 4

Allergens:

Dairy

Dietary Tags:

Gluten-FreeHigh-Protein

Cuisine:

Eastern European

Course:

Main Dish

Tags:

Comfort FoodSoupHeartyRussian Cuisine

Description

A hearty and vibrant beet soup enriched with tender beef, perfect for warming the soul.

Ingredients

  • beef chuck (cut into chunks): 500 grams
  • beets (peeled and grated): 2 medium
  • cabbage (shredded): 2 cups
  • carrots (peeled and grated): 1 large
  • potatoes (diced): 2 medium
  • onion (chopped): 1 large
  • garlic (minced): 3 cloves
  • tomato paste: 2 tablespoons
  • vegetable broth or water: 6 cups
  • sour cream: for serving
  • fresh dill (chopped): for garnish
